reviewText: The first time I saw this video I had checked it out of the public library to review a foreign film for a class I was taking. From the beginning to the end I enjoyed it very much. There were parts that brought tears to my eyes, parts that made me angry at the story line, and parts that keot me in suspense. As far as a foreign film goes, this is a good movie to watch.
Thank you for having search a very good quality dvd. I've juste seen the film and am very happy getting it.
